snippet.title: Believe again [ beatmania COMPLETE MIX, 5keys, Arcade ]
snippet.description: This is the hidden version of "Believe again" from 3rd MIX (except it's in Complete Mix).  Not much difference, but the chart is different.  Evidently they liked the song a lot.
